{"tid":1005154,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為搵到一個更好嘅而同現任分手究竟有冇錯?","createTime":"2019-02-02T04:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T08:32:35.000Z","uid":199757,"like":3,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e009e769ba5d0a42d40d7fade8a2437ccfcea88f","tid":1005154,"uid":199757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:23:30.000Z","msg":"笠定頭盔先 講緊有冇錯 絕對唔係話係啱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假設你同現任一開始拍拖唔係騎牛搵馬心態 而依家有一個異性好接近你 十分曖昧 近乎係一表白就可以拍拖 而佢嘅條件整體都好過你嘅現任 亦都同你現任一樣咁愛你 甚至為你付出更加多 你會唔會同現任分手? (唔準我全都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n成個社會其實都係因為想要得到更好嘅先會進步有更多發明 亦都因為想有更好嘅先會不斷追求更好嘅嘢 好似追新手機 名牌手袋<br />\n<br />\n咁睇法其實分手同更好嘅新嘅一齊又冇錯<br />\n<br />\n但係其實亦都基於當初一齊嘅責任 (再重申 唔係騎牛搵馬心態) 從一而終 大家為大家嘅付出 一分手又會變左賤男賤女 受萬人唾罵<br />\n<br />\n咁睇法又會變左係錯<br />\n<br />\n身邊有d朋友有女都會對其他女性朋友產生好感 或者曖昧 甚至想同現任分手同新嘅一齊 所以諗諗下我都諗到好迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c9b5e555a70cf8c3e4a9d1b5a0ba2de216c1a6","tid":1005154,"uid":199757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"做咩負皮我又唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdaae728a6e77e0bcacc299ffc42615fb7456d14","tid":1005154,"uid":220435,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:28:49.000Z","msg":"同前任分手時handle得好 <br />\n完美交替就冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aeae6b2f1e84bc11967d54ea3f8ed9c1f056aa6","tid":1005154,"uid":232594,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:29:14.000Z","msg":"個女仔知你拍緊拖都埋你身就知唔係好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非個女仔埋你身但你唔話佢知你拍緊拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525e80bfd2c5cafe3c529b568ed863136205849e","tid":1005154,"uid":137960,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:30:18.000Z","msg":"愛情唔係睇條件...<br />\n如果條件好就變心<br />\n咁你根本唔係鍾意你現任，無愛"},{"pid":"ccc056033c557128d29412a194a3dd72129370e2","tid":1005154,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n要走留唔住，要留趕唔走<br />\n<br />\n諗咁多都係無謂<br />\n你需要考慮既係<br />\n你目前鍾唔鍾意呢個女仔"},{"pid":"f0df1f19f07a305fe019e86a7ec35a2dff161775","tid":1005154,"uid":232594,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"525e80bfd2c5cafe3c529b568ed863136205849e","tid":1005154,"uid":137960,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:30:18.000Z","msg":"愛情唔係睇條件...<br />\n如果條件好就變心<br />\n咁你根本唔係鍾意你現任，無愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本樓主當啲女係股票黎，見邊隻有潛力升就沽貨轉買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dde883e5ddc54b26500488ddcd26d4b998d6f89","tid":1005154,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"樓主當拍拖係逐個條件tick/比個分咁<br />\n邊個高分就揀邊個 係唔係?"},{"pid":"4ec26025e82c005b05e32e707865dba4ee3e2673","tid":1005154,"uid":199757,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"7dde883e5ddc54b26500488ddcd26d4b998d6f89","tid":1005154,"uid":313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"樓主當拍拖係逐個條件tick/比個分咁<br />\n邊個高分就揀邊個 係唔係?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:41:36.000Z","msg":"算係 但我一拍拖就唔會想散<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從一而終果種"},{"pid":"59d41bbcb4df943994c4e72b8ee59c882907873a","tid":1005154,"uid":199757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"525e80bfd2c5cafe3c529b568ed863136205849e","tid":1005154,"uid":137960,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:30:18.000Z","msg":"愛情唔係睇條件...<br />\n如果條件好就變心<br />\n咁你根本唔係鍾意你現任，無愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T04:43:52.000Z","msg"